1
00:00:43,040 --> 00:00:50,980
[Sharp Blade in the Snow]

2
00:00:51,050 --> 00:00:54,060
[Episode 22]

3
00:00:55,040 --> 00:00:56,170
Something's wrong.

4
00:00:56,480 --> 00:00:57,600
Since when did Feng Li

5
00:00:57,600 --> 00:00:58,930
turn into such a coward?

6
00:00:59,480 --> 00:01:02,880
Did she hit her head when
she fell into the water or something?

7
00:01:03,040 --> 00:01:05,360
And the Princess Royal's
acting way too nervous…

8
00:01:05,360 --> 00:01:05,840
No.

9
00:01:06,360 --> 00:01:08,220
There's definitely more to this.

10
00:01:14,560 --> 00:01:15,960
How dare you—

11
00:01:16,400 --> 00:01:19,060
storming into the palace
and disrespecting me.

12
00:01:21,760 --> 00:01:23,240
So you're the Young Master of Xiqi,

13
00:01:23,240 --> 00:01:25,039
the one who never shows his face?

14
00:01:25,600 --> 00:01:27,440
Feng Li went to Xiqi once

15
00:01:27,440 --> 00:01:29,160
and came back
a completely different person.

16
00:01:29,160 --> 00:01:30,289
Was this your doing?

17
00:01:30,680 --> 00:01:32,479
Princess Ling, careful with your words.

18
00:01:32,479 --> 00:01:33,840
I am the Queen's

19
00:01:34,080 --> 00:01:36,039
lawful Imperial Consort.

20
00:01:36,120 --> 00:01:37,600
Lawful?

21
00:01:37,920 --> 00:01:39,520
You're nothing but a grotesque coward

22
00:01:39,520 --> 00:01:41,580
who doesn't even dare show your face.

23
00:01:43,840 --> 00:01:45,600
You cherish Feng Li so much?

24
00:01:45,880 --> 00:01:47,400
That really puzzles me.

25
00:01:47,880 --> 00:01:49,720
She's mute now,

26
00:01:49,880 --> 00:01:51,610
and you still want to marry her?

27
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:52,880
Her worth

28
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:55,860
is not something outsiders
could ever understand.

29
00:01:55,920 --> 00:01:57,320
What worth does she have?

30
00:01:57,600 --> 00:01:59,120
Cold-hearted, emotionally distant,

31
00:01:59,120 --> 00:02:00,250
selfish to the core.

32
00:02:01,920 --> 00:02:02,960
Do you even know

33
00:02:03,320 --> 00:02:05,320
that the one originally meant to
marry you in alliance

34
00:02:05,320 --> 00:02:06,720
was me?

35
00:02:28,480 --> 00:02:29,720
Your Highness,

36
00:02:29,880 --> 00:02:31,540
you're beautiful, graceful,

37
00:02:31,600 --> 00:02:32,730
and highly skilled.

38
00:02:33,760 --> 00:02:35,760
To say I felt nothing at all

39
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:37,160
would be a lie.

40
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:40,760
But I have urgent matters today—

41
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:42,800
let's settle this another time.

42
00:02:49,600 --> 00:02:52,060
No wonder Feng Li
was willing to risk her life

43
00:02:52,200 --> 00:02:54,660
and take my place
in the political marriage.

44
00:02:55,079 --> 00:02:57,040
So the young master of Xiqi

45
00:02:57,760 --> 00:02:59,620
does have a bit of charm after all.

46
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:03,800
So this is the plan

47
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:06,000
of the young master of Xiqi—

48
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:08,280
the Queen in one arm,

49
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:10,290
the Princess Ling in the other,

50
00:03:10,520 --> 00:03:12,480
enjoying the best of both worlds.

51
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:16,560
Interesting.

52
00:03:20,079 --> 00:03:21,480
So alike…

53
00:03:23,800 --> 00:03:25,160
Far too alike.

54
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:27,840
Your face

55
00:03:28,760 --> 00:03:30,600
is exactly the same as hers.

56
00:03:31,880 --> 00:03:33,120
Do you know that

57
00:03:33,280 --> 00:03:34,680
Feng Li's mother—

58
00:03:34,720 --> 00:03:36,040
the former Queen of Mocheng—

59
00:03:36,040 --> 00:03:37,320
my elder sister,

60
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:39,329
was unmatched in beauty and grace.

61
00:03:39,480 --> 00:03:40,920
We looked

62
00:03:40,920 --> 00:03:42,480
identical.

63
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:45,240
Yet all the world revered her,

64
00:03:45,480 --> 00:03:46,400
while I

65
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:48,600
could only live as her shadow—

66
00:03:49,920 --> 00:03:52,000
a princess

67
00:03:52,680 --> 00:03:53,810
buried in darkness.

68
00:03:56,680 --> 00:03:57,760
And you?

69
00:03:58,440 --> 00:04:00,900
Born a lowly commoner,
the lowest of the low,

70
00:04:01,240 --> 00:04:03,440
yet now you wear Feng Li's name,

71
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:05,520
enjoy her honor,

72
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:07,250
and even become her betrothed.

73
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:09,680
Same face,

74
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,600
different fate.

75
00:04:14,200 --> 00:04:14,680
Come.

76
00:04:15,200 --> 00:04:16,529
Let me help you dress up.

77
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:18,200
You're getting married,

78
00:04:18,200 --> 00:04:20,519
so naturally you should look magnificent.

79
00:04:20,519 --> 00:04:21,959
Let all of Mocheng—

80
00:04:22,280 --> 00:04:23,410
let the whole world—

81
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:24,760
remember this.

82
00:04:37,080 --> 00:04:38,409
This belongs to Feng Li.

83
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:40,260
You're not worthy to touch it!

84
00:04:44,640 --> 00:04:45,920
As long as you behave

85
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:46,920
and don't move,

86
00:04:48,080 --> 00:04:49,640
all the glory of this world

87
00:04:50,120 --> 00:04:51,480
will be yours.

88
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:07,640
Not bad,

89
00:05:08,080 --> 00:05:09,340
you look just like her.

90
00:05:10,720 --> 00:05:12,480
Once the wedding day arrives,

91
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:15,690
once Phoenix Incense and the Tiger Tally
are in my hands—

92
00:05:15,960 --> 00:05:16,720
Sister,

93
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:19,440
I'll finally be just like you.

94
00:05:19,880 --> 00:05:20,960
Your throne,

95
00:05:21,400 --> 00:05:22,400
your husband,

96
00:05:22,760 --> 00:05:23,820
and your daughter,

97
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:25,600
will all be mine.

98
00:05:26,760 --> 00:05:28,280
For this day,

99
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:31,120
I killed my sister's husband

100
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:34,060
and cast Feng Li out into the wilderness.

101
00:05:34,480 --> 00:05:36,520
More than ten years of patience

102
00:05:37,600 --> 00:05:39,640
will finally come to an end.

103
00:05:40,280 --> 00:05:41,320
So it was you,

104
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:42,800
Meng Wu.

105
00:05:43,880 --> 00:05:46,080
You were the one who killed my father.

106
00:05:47,880 --> 00:05:48,840
Good girl,

107
00:05:49,640 --> 00:05:52,500
as long as you cooperate
and finish this act with me,

108
00:05:52,840 --> 00:05:54,720
I will make everyone believe

109
00:05:55,320 --> 00:05:55,960
that you

110
00:05:56,280 --> 00:05:57,960
are the real Feng Li.

111
00:06:04,520 --> 00:06:06,450
You arrived later than I expected.

112
00:06:07,080 --> 00:06:08,840
The outcome is already decided;

113
00:06:08,840 --> 00:06:10,500
there is no need to be anxious.

114
00:06:12,200 --> 00:06:13,000
Okay.

115
00:06:15,560 --> 00:06:17,040
On the wedding day,

116
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:19,560
once Phoenix Incense,

117
00:06:19,560 --> 00:06:21,840
the Phoenix Seal,
and the Tiger Tally are all in hand,

118
00:06:21,840 --> 00:06:23,640
I will lead our Dongli loyalists

119
00:06:23,840 --> 00:06:25,300
and strike from all sides,

120
00:06:25,920 --> 00:06:27,200
to avenge my father

121
00:06:27,320 --> 00:06:28,400
and my country.

122
00:06:37,080 --> 00:06:38,409
What are we waiting for?

123
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:42,960
Your plan is excellent, Your Highness,

124
00:06:42,960 --> 00:06:43,800
but I

125
00:06:44,360 --> 00:06:46,120
have a better strategy.

126
00:06:47,680 --> 00:06:48,610
What do you mean?

127
00:06:50,440 --> 00:06:52,170
Are you betraying our country?

128
00:06:56,280 --> 00:06:57,240
Your Highness,

129
00:06:58,560 --> 00:07:00,560
Dongli no longer exists,

130
00:07:01,040 --> 00:07:02,840
so how can I betray it?

131
00:07:03,520 --> 00:07:04,480
Rather,

132
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:07,960
I have simply chosen a safer path.

133
00:07:09,400 --> 00:07:10,200
How dare you!

134
00:07:16,080 --> 00:07:17,280
Come to think of it,

135
00:07:18,080 --> 00:07:19,560
the success of planting

136
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:21,620
the fake Queen in the palace this time

137
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:24,760
was largely thanks to you, Your Highness.

138
00:07:25,880 --> 00:07:29,140
Had you not willingly cooperated,
letting her be isolated

139
00:07:29,920 --> 00:07:32,480
and drawing the attention
of the people of Xiqi away,

140
00:07:32,480 --> 00:07:34,740
how could the plan have gone so smoothly?

141
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:36,880
I plotted against Feng Li

142
00:07:37,880 --> 00:07:39,440
to restore our Dongli,

143
00:07:40,720 --> 00:07:42,520
not to satisfy your personal ambitions.

144
00:07:42,520 --> 00:07:43,850
What's the difference?

145
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:49,560
You should rest easy

146
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:51,290
and remain here in this prison.

147
00:07:51,480 --> 00:07:53,760
Once I have full control of the situation,

148
00:07:53,760 --> 00:07:55,040
I will be sure to

149
00:07:57,320 --> 00:07:58,960
leave you a memorial tablet.

150
00:08:13,560 --> 00:08:14,360
Come out!

151
00:08:18,200 --> 00:08:20,260
So you are the crown prince of Dongli.

152
00:08:20,440 --> 00:08:22,400
You and Lu Ran worked together

153
00:08:22,400 --> 00:08:23,860
to scheme against Feng Li.

154
00:08:25,680 --> 00:08:26,960
You were hiding there just now

155
00:08:26,960 --> 00:08:28,220
and heard everything.

156
00:08:28,560 --> 00:08:30,360
Yes, I am the crown prince of Dongli,

157
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:32,400
but I never meant to harm Feng Li.

158
00:08:32,520 --> 00:08:33,919
You hid your identity,

159
00:08:34,039 --> 00:08:35,770
deliberately got close to her,

160
00:08:35,880 --> 00:08:37,120
deceived her trust,

161
00:08:37,520 --> 00:08:39,679
and even allowed her
to be taken away by Lu Ran.

162
00:08:39,679 --> 00:08:42,480
And you still dare say
you never wanted to hurt her?

163
00:08:44,760 --> 00:08:45,800
This was

164
00:08:47,360 --> 00:08:48,520
my miscalculation.

165
00:08:49,120 --> 00:08:50,180
Lu Ran deceived me.

166
00:08:50,720 --> 00:08:52,320
He claimed loyalty on the surface,

167
00:08:52,320 --> 00:08:55,180
but in secret
he had long pledged himself to Meng Wu.

168
00:08:55,720 --> 00:08:58,180
Now the two of them
are working hand in glove.

169
00:08:58,200 --> 00:08:59,330
The one in the palace

170
00:08:59,800 --> 00:09:01,130
is nothing but a puppet.

171
00:09:03,280 --> 00:09:05,480
How dare you speak so casually about it?

172
00:09:05,640 --> 00:09:06,440
Then tell me,

173
00:09:06,800 --> 00:09:08,560
where is the real Feng Li?

174
00:09:11,840 --> 00:09:12,680
I don't know.

175
00:09:13,560 --> 00:09:14,890
After she was switched,

176
00:09:15,280 --> 00:09:16,740
she never appeared again.

177
00:09:18,040 --> 00:09:18,800
Now,

178
00:09:19,520 --> 00:09:21,760
Lu Ran and Meng Wu
are laying traps everywhere.

179
00:09:21,760 --> 00:09:23,620
Even I have been imprisoned here.

180
00:09:25,800 --> 00:09:27,530
As for where the real Feng Li is,

181
00:09:27,760 --> 00:09:29,760
I am afraid only the two of them know.

182
00:09:31,040 --> 00:09:32,240
What should I do then?

183
00:09:33,480 --> 00:09:34,400
Aunt?

184
00:09:35,800 --> 00:09:37,320
Meng Wu is already arranging the wedding

185
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:40,250
between that mute woman
and the young master of Xiqi.

186
00:09:40,320 --> 00:09:41,400
If we are any later,

187
00:09:41,960 --> 00:09:42,960
Feng Li's identity

188
00:09:42,960 --> 00:09:44,480
will truly be stolen.

189
00:09:45,520 --> 00:09:47,180
If you really want to save her,

190
00:09:47,920 --> 00:09:49,720
go find the young master of Xiqi,

191
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:51,160
Xin Yao?

192
00:09:52,440 --> 00:09:53,520
Would he help us?

193
00:09:54,560 --> 00:09:55,840
Back in Xiqi,

194
00:09:56,080 --> 00:09:56,720
Xin Yao

195
00:09:57,200 --> 00:09:58,960
and Feng Li formed an alliance.

196
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:00,730
Now, apart from him,

197
00:10:01,480 --> 00:10:02,680
you have no one else you can trust.

198
00:10:02,680 --> 00:10:04,210
But he is still an outsider.

199
00:10:06,320 --> 00:10:08,580
He is Feng Li's Imperial Consort in name.

200
00:10:09,040 --> 00:10:11,000
If you were the young master of Xiqi,

201
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:12,080
would you be willing

202
00:10:12,080 --> 00:10:13,410
to marry a counterfeit?

203
00:10:21,320 --> 00:10:23,520
If you could sneak in, you can sneak out.

204
00:10:23,520 --> 00:10:24,160
Go find Xin Yao,

205
00:10:24,160 --> 00:10:24,800
hurry!

206
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:33,760
Here.

207
00:10:34,240 --> 00:10:35,680
This is what I made today.

208
00:10:36,080 --> 00:10:37,740
It is finer than yesterday's.

209
00:10:46,040 --> 00:10:47,700
To see you smile at me like this

210
00:10:47,720 --> 00:10:49,040
feels like a dream.

211
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:50,770
It's wonderful.

212
00:10:56,360 --> 00:10:57,480
In five days,

213
00:10:58,240 --> 00:11:00,640
it will be the wedding
of the Queen of Mocheng

214
00:11:00,640 --> 00:11:02,520
and the young master of Xiqi.

215
00:11:03,640 --> 00:11:04,970
But what does it matter?

216
00:11:06,080 --> 00:11:07,080
You are

217
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:08,840
no longer

218
00:11:09,120 --> 00:11:10,760
the lofty Queen.

219
00:11:12,520 --> 00:11:13,720
You are my Li.

220
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:17,680
Once the wedding is over,

221
00:11:18,400 --> 00:11:19,800
we will leave the palace.

222
00:11:20,640 --> 00:11:21,360
We will go somewhere

223
00:11:21,360 --> 00:11:22,560
no one knows us,

224
00:11:23,520 --> 00:11:24,680
open a small shop,

225
00:11:25,920 --> 00:11:27,050
plant some flowers,

226
00:11:27,600 --> 00:11:28,930
and sell a few pastries.

227
00:11:29,800 --> 00:11:31,130
We will rise with the sun

228
00:11:31,920 --> 00:11:33,120
and rest at dusk,

229
00:11:34,320 --> 00:11:35,680
living like the most ordinary couple

230
00:11:35,680 --> 00:11:36,760
in this world.

231
00:11:42,160 --> 00:11:42,960
In the future,

232
00:11:43,520 --> 00:11:44,440
I will take you to find

233
00:11:44,440 --> 00:11:45,720
the finest healers.

234
00:11:49,280 --> 00:11:49,960
I know

235
00:11:50,480 --> 00:11:52,210
your throat was badly injured.

236
00:11:52,640 --> 00:11:54,170
If it truly cannot be cured,

237
00:11:54,880 --> 00:11:55,940
it does not matter.

238
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:58,480
My Li

239
00:11:59,480 --> 00:12:00,400
only needs to

240
00:12:00,960 --> 00:12:01,720
smile at me.

241
00:12:06,680 --> 00:12:07,880
You used to be

242
00:12:08,680 --> 00:12:09,680
so tired.

243
00:12:11,040 --> 00:12:12,500
Back then, perhaps Feng Li

244
00:12:13,120 --> 00:12:15,180
had already grown weary of the palace

245
00:12:15,840 --> 00:12:17,200
and all those schemes.

246
00:12:19,960 --> 00:12:21,760
Now that you are willing to stay,

247
00:12:22,400 --> 00:12:23,800
is it because, deep down,

248
00:12:24,400 --> 00:12:26,260
you already have me in your heart?

249
00:12:38,240 --> 00:12:39,040
Li,

250
00:12:40,280 --> 00:12:41,160
thank you.

251
00:12:42,160 --> 00:12:43,290
Having you by my side

252
00:12:44,400 --> 00:12:45,240
is wonderful.

253
00:12:49,600 --> 00:12:50,920
This madman

254
00:12:51,240 --> 00:12:53,040
is deeply in love with the Queen.

255
00:12:53,320 --> 00:12:54,080
So be it.

256
00:12:54,440 --> 00:12:56,600
As long as I act well and am not exposed,

257
00:12:56,760 --> 00:12:58,440
he will never bear to kill me.

258
00:12:58,760 --> 00:13:00,680
Then I can remain his Feng Li,

259
00:13:00,840 --> 00:13:03,040
enjoying a lifetime of wealth and glory

260
00:13:03,320 --> 00:13:04,480
with ease.
